      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-deploy-app/pick-apply-run.59e7c43d.mp3",
      "narrationText": "流程很简单：选一个模板、应用到 repo，然后运行。CLI 自带内置模板，所以我们永远不必从头写 docker-compose。",
      "audioDurationSec": 14.28898
